dev.nokee.ide.xcode

Interface XcodeIdeWorkspaceExtension

  • All Superinterfaces:
    XcodeIdeProjectExtension

    public interface XcodeIdeWorkspaceExtension
extends XcodeIdeProjectExtension
    The configuration for mapping a Gradle project to Xcode projects and workspace. The workspace extension is register to the Project instance only for the root project where the Xcode IDE plugin is applied. The project extension, that is XcodeIdeProjectExtension, is register to sub-projects instead.
    Since:
    0.3
